            <title>[AMQ-1781] LDAP + JAAS = NullPointerException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-1781</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If an attempt is made to configure the LDAPLoginModule JAAS plugin, as per the instructions inside either of these two messages, ActiveMQ refuses to start with the NullPointerException reported below.&lt;/p&gt;

